    "SUMMARY": "Sascha Stegemann (born 6 December 1984) is a German football referee who is based in Niederkassel. He referees for 1. FC Niederkassel of the Middle Rhine Football Association. He is a FIFA referee, and is ranked as a UEFA first category referee."
